      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，颜色区分很好。流程上Alice先调用合约的makeTradeInvitation，参数带上HealthTech_LabAnalyzer，然后合约要激活，再异步通知Zoe发起makeInvitation，目标是HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault。",
